{"tid":1328747,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「共享中國人榮耀」小米5月派股ARK Trust 昨始披露","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T16:03:33.000Z","uid":104138,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1474679aade6512f4c1949a3f9520319ec52a204","tid":1328747,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:14:40.000Z","msg":"小米集團（1810）在今年5月再向主要股東ARK Trust （Hong Kong） Limited派發獎勵股份，但直至昨日才向聯交所披露，ARK Trust持股比例增至27.87％。<br />\n<br />\n為獎勵股份 持股增至近28%<br />\n據聯交所數據，小米在今年5月27日再向ARK Trust派發約17.35億股股份，但大股東知悉有關事件或股份權益的日期是7月10日，而直至昨日集團才披露有關交易。在交易發生後，ARK Trust持股比例由17.62％增加至27.87％。<br />\n<br />\n在小米上市前，創辦人雷軍的全部權益均透過ARK Trust以受託人身分持有，但上市後有其他股份獎勵計劃的受益人成為ARK Trust客戶，故ARK Trust不再只代表雷軍。而是次派發股份，集團並沒有披露受益人的最終身分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20190717/s00004/1563301426630/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B35%E6%9C%88%E6%B4%BE%E8%82%A1ark-trust-%E6%98%A8%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00004%2F1563301426630%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B35%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%2582%25A1ark-trust-%25E6%2598%25A8%25E5%25A7%258B%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakqy4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=2b264cd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20190717%2Fs00004%2F1563301426630%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B35%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%2582%25A1ark-trust-%25E6%2598%25A8%25E5%25A7%258B%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2&h=e047751c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20190717/s00004/1563301426630/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B35%E6%9C%88%E6%B4%BE%E8%82%A1ark-trust-%E6%98%A8%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2</a>"},{"pid":"3579325e8b87f427bb81b20a2e9a3b8b606947ae","tid":1328747,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-1